# Environment Variables Template

## Required for Production

### Site Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://grootanalytics.com

### SEO & Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=your_verification_code_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_GTM_ID=GTM-XXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

### Error Tracking (Sentry)
SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@sentry.io/xxx
SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=your_sentry_auth_token
SENTRY_ORG=your_org_name
SENTRY_PROJECT=groot-frontend
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_RELEASE=production

### Email Service (for contact form)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.sendgrid.net
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=apikey
SMTP_PASSWORD=your_sendgrid_api_key
SMTP_FROM=noreply@grootanalytics.com
CONTACT_EMAIL=contact@grootanalytics.com

### reCAPTCHA (for spam protection)
NEXT_PUBLIC_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your_site_key
RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key

### CMS (if using)
# CONTENTFUL_SPACE_ID=your_space_id
# CONTENTFUL_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_access_token
# CONTENTFUL_PREVIEW_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_preview_token

### Database (if needed)
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/database

## Optional

### Feature Flags
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_AB_TESTING=false
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAINTENANCE_MODE=false

### Third-party Integrations
# HUBSPOT_API_KEY=your_hubspot_key
# LINKEDIN_PIXEL_ID=your_pixel_id
# FACEBOOK_PIXEL_ID=your_pixel_id

### Performance Monitoring
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SPEEDCURVE_LUX_ID=your_lux_id

## Development Only

### Debug
DEBUG=false
NEXT_PUBLIC_DEBUG_MODE=false

### Local Testing
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
